{"ts":"2026-04-02T12:36:59.385Z","event":"readme_summary","data":{"maxChars":600,"cleanedChars":5047,"summaryChars":556,"keywords":["---","ott","scout","watch","discovery","using","every","vector","api","backend","personalized","streaming","tmdb","supabase","inference","ensuring","now","filtering"],"highlights":["![Hero Image](./assets/hero.png)","**Conversational Discovery**: Chat with the built-in AI scout using natural language (\"Gritty crime thrillers like Mirzapur but in English\"). High-performance inference ensures near-instant responses.","**Zero-Noise Filtering**: Connect your OTT platforms (Netflix, Prime, Hotstar, JioCinema, etc.). The app hides anything you can't stream, ensuring every recommendation is actionable.","**Personalized Newsletters**: Receive a weekly digest of top 5 hand-picked recommendations delivered straight to your inbox via **Resend**.","**Sleek Dark Mode**: A gorgeous, glassmorphic interface designed for cinematic immersion using **Tailwind CSS v4**.","**Real-time Tracing**: Integrated with **Langfuse** to track every step of the recommendation pipeline. View live traces at the [Project Dashboard](https://cloud.langfuse.com/project/cmmu985wg044zad08l2v1s4f7).","OTT Scout uses a multi-stage **Hybrid Intelligence** pipeline to ensure your feed is never stale:","| Layer | Technologies |","**Node.js** (v18+) & **Python** (3.10+)","---","<div align=\"center\">","This project is open-source. Feel free to fork, submit PRs, and build the future of streaming discovery!","🎬 OTT Scout: AI-Powered Personalized Streaming 🍿","**Taste Synthesis**: Every interaction (Like, Dislike, Watch) builds a complex multidimensional profile of your preferences using state-of-the-art vector embeddings.","**Bias-Free Diversity**: Specifically optimized to balance genres and languages, ensuring high-quality Hindi and regional content gets equal spotlight alongside global blockbusters.","**Direct-to-Platform Routing**: Skip the manual search. Our **\"Watch Now\"** system generates deep-search links that drop you directly into the search bar of your favorite streaming service.","**Actionable Links**: Every email includes one-click \"Watch Now\" buttons that sync with your session for a seamless cross-device experience.","**Skeleton Loaders**: Fast, glitch-free loading states for a smooth browsing experience."]}}
