{"ts":"2026-04-06T08:28:05.293Z","event":"readme_summary","data":{"maxChars":600,"cleanedChars":5047,"summaryChars":536,"keywords":["---","ott","scout","watch","discovery","using","every","vector","api","backend","personalized","streaming","tmdb","supabase","inference","ensuring","now","filtering"],"highlights":["🎬 OTT Scout: AI-Powered Personalized Streaming 🍿","🔥 Key Features","🧠 Deep-Taste AI Engine","**Conversational Discovery**: Chat with the built-in AI scout using natural language (\"Gritty crime thrillers like Mirzapur but in English\"). High-performance inference ensures near-instant responses.","📺 Subscription-First \"Watch Now\"","**Zero-Noise Filtering**: Connect your OTT platforms (Netflix, Prime, Hotstar, JioCinema, etc.). The app hides anything you can't stream, ensuring every recommendation is actionable.","📧 Weekly Scout Automations","**Personalized Newsletters**: Receive a weekly digest of top 5 hand-picked recommendations delivered straight to your inbox via **Resend**.","⚡ Premium UI/UX","**Sleek Dark Mode**: A gorgeous, glassmorphic interface designed for cinematic immersion using **Tailwind CSS v4**.","🕵️ AI Observability & Monitoring","**Real-time Tracing**: Integrated with **Langfuse** to track every step of the recommendation pipeline. View live traces at the [Project Dashboard](https://cloud.langfuse.com/project/cmmu985wg044zad08l2v1s4f7).","🛠️ Technical Spotlight: The Recommendation Pipeline","🛠️ Technology Stack","🚀 Speed-Start Guide","1. Prerequisites","**Node.js** (v18+) & **Python** (3.10+)","2. Backend Setup"]}}
